cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.SY 

The paper discusses security issues related to cloud computing, specifically Distributed Denial of Service (DDoS) attacks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
